E4Plus1.uk.description: A Totally Fun Thing Bart Will Never Do Again: Bart sees an ad for the ultimate cruise, begs his parents for a holiday, and then tries to make the vacation last forever. (S23 Ep19/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Spy Who Learned Me: While he's on sick leave, Homer learns how to be a better husband, with the help of dashing spy movie crime fighter Stradivarius Cain (Bryan Cranston). (S23 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Scavenger Vortex: Raj organises an epic and demanding scavenger hunt, designed to test the friends' scientific knowledge and common sense. (S7 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Raiders Minimization: Amy ruins one of Sheldon's favourite films by pointing out a flaw in the storyline. Raj and Stuart decide to create online dating profiles. (S7 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: See You Next Fall: The family gather at Jay's before heading to Alex's middle school graduation ceremony. While they're there, Jay tries to hide a Botox mishap from everyone. (S2 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: The One That Got Away: Jay wants a quiet birthday fishing on the lake, but the family think he wants a big celebration. (S2 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Maternal Combustion: Personalities collide when Sheldon and Leonard's mothers finally meet. Howard decides to 'man up' and do his share of the housework. (S8 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Commitment Determination: Sheldon pressures Leonard and Penny to choose a date for their wedding while dealing with changes in his own relationship. (S8 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Matrimonial Momentum: Penny struggles with Leonard's confession that he kissed another woman. Sheldon doesn't know how to act when Amy breaks up with him. (S9 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Separation Oscillation: Sheldon films a special post-break-up episode of Fun with Flags. Bernadette feels guilty about withholding a secret from Penny. (S9 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: DFW: Peralta invites his newly discovered half-sister Kate to come and stay with him and Santiago. But she's a bit of a nightmare. (S5 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gray Star Mutual: A fire destroys Boyle's food truck, Diaz helps Santiago pick her wedding dress, and Gina and Jeffords coach Holt in the art of social media. (S5 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Little Big Mom: When Marge breaks her leg in a skiing accident, Lisa takes over running the Simpson household, and Homer and Bart end up moving to a leper colony in Hawaii. (S11 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Faith Off: Homer gets a bucket of superglue stuck to his head and the only person who can remove it is a preacher (Don Cheadle), who inspires Bart to become a faith healer. (S11 Ep11/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Instant sparks fly in a passionate ceremony as our final couple get wed. And as the in-laws keep coming, one bride falls short for a frustrated friend. (S10 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Solder Excursion Diversion: Sheldon makes a surprise revelation when Amy buys him a new laptop. Leonard and Howard lie to their wives to avoid an errand. (S9 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Big Bear Precipitation: Sheldon shares a secret about Leonard when the two of them go on a weekend trip to a cabin in the country with Amy and Penny. (S9 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bart of War: Bart and Milhouse are caught getting up to no good in Ned Flanders' house and are enrolled in separate clubs to keep them off the streets. (S14 Ep21/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Moe Baby Blues: Moe becomes Maggie's babysitter after saving her from a car accident when he was about to end it all. She gives him a reason to live, but Homer isn't happy. (S14 Ep22/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Wedding for Disaster: Homer and Marge discover that they're not officially married when Reverend Lovejoy finds out he wasn't a licensed minister at the time of their ceremony. (S20 Ep15/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Opposites A-Frack: Lisa calls on politician Maxine Lombard to stop Mr Burns' secret fracking operation but is taken aback when Lombard and Burns are attracted to each other. (S26 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dan puts a broken engagement behind him on a date with personal trainer Jess, whose love life needs a workout. And Burnley carpet salesman Nathan bids to turn over a new leaf. (S19 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics have been watching Squid Game, Strictly Come Dancing, The Mating Game, Family Fortunes, Extreme Food Phobics, and The Hairy Bikers Go North. (S18 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the 'Box this time: I'm a Celebrity... Get Me Out of Here!, Tiger King 2, An Audience with Adele, Michael McIntyre's The Wheel, Close to Me, and BBC/ITV News (Austria). (S18 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Open House: The Great Sex
E4Plus1.uk.description: Experiment: Alex and Alana want to open up, but can they overcome intense jealousy? And could an orgy be the best way for Jonny and Sarah to finally open up their relationship? (S3 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Three Gays of the Condo: After realising that Marge only married him because she was pregnant with Bart, Homer moves out and ends up sharing an apartment with two gay men. (S14 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dude, Where's My Ranch?: After Homer has a hit record with an anti-Ned Flanders Christmas carol, the family decide to get away from it all at a ranch. (S14 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rick and Morty [adult swim]
E4Plus1.uk.description: Star Mort Rickturn of the Jerri: The season finale is a family adventure with an invisibility belt - but can a family that disappears together, stay together? (S4 Ep10/10) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Robot Chicken: DC Comics...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Special I: Robot Chicken characters join the DC Comics universe to poke fun at the heroes with the most impressive powers - and the ones who aren't really superheroes at all.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Below Deck Sailing Yacht
E4Plus1.uk.description: Tender Bender: Gary crashes the tender. Danni and Keith continue to flirt, but a cute host catches Danni's eye. And Gary and Daisy's friendship is still rocky. (S5 Ep2/16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Viewing Party Combustion: During a get-together to watch TV at the flat, a minor argument between Sheldon and Leonard escalates into a heated debate. (S9 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fermentation Bifurcation: The gang run into Penny's ex-boyfriend, Zack, at a wine bar. Bernadette, who can't drink, hangs out with Sheldon. (S9 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Treehouse: Gloria persuades Jay to commit to a night of salsa dancing after seeing how much his friend Shorty and his girlfriend do together. Phil builds a tree house for Luke. (S3 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Finding Fizbo: Cam is enraged when he sees a clip of someone desecrating his beloved Fizbo costume, so he sets out on a quest to restore Fizbo's good name. (S8 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Caf Kingston: In California, Gordon visits Jamaican restaurant Caf Kingston. He meets micromanaging owner Dr Una Morris, who's also a radiotherapist. (S4 Ep11) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ringmaster Keifth: Cam tries to make up for his Thanksgiving debacle by hosting a New Year feast. And Phil's not sure how to feel about his dad dating his childhood babysitter. (S8 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sarge & Pea: Cam is incensed when a rude parent robs him of a precious Lily moment during her dance recital. Jay, Claire and Mitch unexpectedly run into Dede at a family wedding. (S8 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip featuring animals and food, from the always hilarious Tube that is Rude.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Capri: In Eagle Rock, California, Gordon helps Capri, a restaurant in a rut that's owned by identical twins Jim and Jeff and is closed more often than it's open. (S4 Ep12) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gordon Ramsay revisits three restaurants - Mojito, The Junction (formerly Flamangos) and Bazzini - to check in with the owners. Is he pleased with their progress? (S4 Ep13) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Beyond Blunderdome: Mel Gibson hires Homer to help him rewrite his remake of Mr Smith Goes to Washington. (S11 Ep1/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brother's Little Helper: An experimental ADHD drug improves Bart's behaviour but makes him paranoid: is Major League Baseball using a satellite to read his thoughts? (S11 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Workplace Proximity: Amy tells Sheldon she's been asked to work on a project at his university, but the guys insist that it will be bad for their relationship. (S7 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Romance Resonance: Sheldon is mortified when he stumbles upon an important scientific breakthrough by accident. Howard makes a romantic gesture to Bernadette. (S7 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dude Ranch: The family don their cowboy boots and hats and head to Jackson Hole, Wyoming, for some fun and adventure in the great outdoors. (S3 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bachelor Party Corrosion: The guys' science skills are tested when they get a flat tyre during Leonard's surprise bachelor party weekend in Mexico. (S9 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The 2003 Approximation: Sheldon sulks when Penny and Leonard announce that they're moving in together. Howard and Raj form a band to play at the comic book shop. (S9 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Perspiration Implementation: The guys take fencing lessons from Barry Kripke. Stuart struggles to attract female customers to the comic book shop. (S9 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Helium Insufficiency: Sheldon and Leonard struggle to find the supplies they need for an experiment. Penny and Bernadette download a dating app for Amy. (S9 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bachelor/ette Party: Boyle organises an elaborate scavenger hunt for Peralta's bachelor party, but the guys take short cuts that throw the event into disarray. (S5 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Show Me Going: The squad worry about Diaz when she responds to an active shooter alert. (S5 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Mansion Family: Mr Burns leaves town for a full medical check-up, leaving the Simpsons in charge of his mansion. Guest starring Britney Spears as herself. (S11 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Saddlesore Galactica: Homer and Bart save a horse from the fair and decide to train him as an American footballer. Or maybe a racehorse. (S11 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Line Substitution Solution: Sheldon pays Stuart to spend the afternoon shopping with Amy so that he can queue up to see a special film screening instead. (S9 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Convergence Convergence: Conflict arises when Leonard's recently divorced parents and Sheldon's devoutly religious mother are all in town at the same time. (S9 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Conjugal Conjecture: The gang face an awkward morning after Sheldon's mother and Leonard's father share an evening together. Penny's family arrive in town. (S10 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Military Miniaturization: Howard has a meeting with Air Force representative Colonel Williams about the gyroscope he invented with Leonard and Sheldon. (S10 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Girl Who Slept Too Little: Lisa becomes plagued by nightmares when the council move the cemetery next door to the Simpsons' house. (S17 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Eeny Teeny Maya Moe: Homer takes Maggie to Moe's and accidentally leaves her in the playground outside the bar. Meanwhile, Moe's delighted to get to know a woman online. (S20 Ep16/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Simpsorama: In a crossover episode, the Simpsons meet the Planet Express crew from Futurama, who've travelled through time to present-day Springfield to stop a catastrophe. (S26 Ep6/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Will Natasha's quick wit give stand-up comedian Mani a run for his money? And is it game over for Nintendo geek Lewis when he reveals his extreme love of gaming to his date? (S19 Ep2)
